{"tid":1612563,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[求大家]停一停 諗一諗","createTime":"2019-10-02T09:38:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-03T08:40:55.000Z","uid":137699,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"a07be1cc59a7bb8fc9783c635366e37db598f937","tid":1612563,"uid":137699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T09:38:37.000Z","msg":"10.1 發生左好多事 好多核彈 <br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">但係我地根本冇充分發揮威力</span></span></strong> <br />\n要集中煲大幾件事 要用輿論 用文宣 <br />\n<br />\n琴晚到今朝 有唔同既人提出唔同既活動 但係<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">冇一個</span></span></strong>係可以召集到多人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">點解我地唔做足文宣 吹行曬雞 先行動？</span></span></strong><br />\n你幾個鐘前先做文宣 邊有可能叫得多人出黎？仲要分散地區搞？ 每區又冇planning咁 最後可能每個地區得幾十人 到時咩氣勢都冇曬啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 只係白白消費緊10.1發生既事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲有咁多位手足都唔係鐵打 你連續幾日吹行曬雞 體力會消耗得好嚴重<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">與其少人行動 人丁單薄 我寧願真係做足文宣 人人都知行動細節 人多勢眾咁行出黎 話比全世界知香港人唔會認輸！</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n我知大家好嬲 但係咁係唔夠 我地係要全香港既人知道發生緊咩事 要全香港既人都嬲 都一齊出黎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">做足文宣 <br />\n凝聚全人 <br />\n做足準備 <br />\n今個星期日再出黎</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">光復香港 時代革命<br />\n五大訴求 缺一不可</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"aa5ca7ff51eaf726d6fcd129ca5e57d4aad5657e","tid":1612563,"uid":137699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":